OL,2,MThe Xelatype: a journey through time
OL,4,Mand space
OL,6,CTim Jacobs (aka mitxela)
OL,7,CSun 16:40-17:10
OL,8,CStage C
OL,10,GIn my quest for Weird Art, long have I
OL,11,Gwanted to build a digital slit-scan
OL,12,Gcamera. The idea was to take a linear
OL,13,GCCD, a load of RAM, and glue them
OL,14,Gtogether with an FPGA. But as I
OL,15,Gpursued the project, things went in a
OL,16,Gstrange new direction, and I ended up
OL,17,Gcreating something different,
OL,18,Gsomething so fascinatingly odd that it
OL,19,Gchanged the way I think about time and
OL,20,Gspace. It all got quite philosophical.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
